<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:19:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：消息人士称，俄罗斯与中国的首次易货贸易可能会在今年秋季进行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/first-russia-china-barter-trade-may-come-this-autumn-sources-say-2024-08-08/</link><description>三位贸易和支付消息人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯和中国可能开始使用易货贸易计划，其中两位预计最早将于今年秋天达成涉及农业的交易，因为莫斯科和北京试图限制使用受美国监控的银行系统。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/first-russia-china-barter-trade-may-come-this-autumn-sources-say-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国超越中国成为德国最大贸易伙伴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/us-tops-china-germanys-biggest-trading-partner-2024-08-08/</link><description>德国统计局的初步数据显示，美国在 2024 年上半年取代中国成为德国最大的贸易伙伴，在美国经济强劲的背景下，柏林减少对北京依赖的努力逐渐成形。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/us-tops-china-germanys-biggest-trading-partner-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美联储放松押注、套利交易平仓让分析师看好亚洲货币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/fed-easing-bets-carry-trade-unwind-turn-analysts-bullish-asian-currencies-2024-08-08/</link><description>路透调查发现，由于美联储降息押注增加以及日元融资套利交易平仓，分析师一年多来首次看好大多数亚洲主要货币。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 05:49:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/fed-easing-bets-carry-trade-unwind-turn-analysts-bullish-asian-currencies-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>名爵汽车将在墨西哥建设制造工厂和研发中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-motor-build-manufacturing-plant-rd-center-mexico-2024-08-08/</link><description>名爵汽车周三表示，计划在墨西哥建立一家制造工厂和一个研发中心，并补充说，这将带来收集拉丁美洲特定市场情报的额外好处。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:54:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-motor-build-manufacturing-plant-rd-center-mexico-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>媒体报道称，韩国要求电动汽车制造商在火灾后披露电池品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/south-korea-require-ev-makers-disclose-battery-brands-after-fire-media-report-2024-08-08/</link><description>据一家报纸周四报道，韩国计划要求电动汽车 (EV) 制造商披露汽车电池的品牌，原因是地下停车场的一辆汽车起火，造成大面积损坏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/south-korea-require-ev-makers-disclose-battery-brands-after-fire-media-report-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>日本资生堂成为最新受中国经济衰退打击的奢侈品牌，股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/japans-shiseido-becomes-latest-luxury-brand-hit-by-china-slump-shares-plunge-2024-08-08/</link><description>日本化妆品巨头资生堂周四在东京交易中跌停，此前其年中盈利受到重组成本和中国需求下滑的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/japans-shiseido-becomes-latest-luxury-brand-hit-by-china-slump-shares-plunge-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中方敦促ITA加强对美国运动员的检测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-urges-ita-intensify-testing-us-athletes-2024-08-08/</link><description>在美国短跑运动员埃里扬·奈顿(Erriyon Knighton)违禁物质群勃龙检测呈阳性后，中国反兴奋剂机构(CHINADA)周四敦促国际检测机构(ITA)加强对美国田径运动员的检测。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-urges-ita-intensify-testing-us-athletes-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>科技股拖累亚洲股市波动，日元在波动性交易中上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市在涨跌之间反弹，而日元和美国债券则试图反弹，因为全球投资者在市场疯狂的一周中努力寻找立足点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>交易员思考日本疯狂一周的利率走势，日元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-firms-after-sharp-drop-traders-assess-japans-rate-path-2024-08-08/</link><description>日元在动荡的一周中前一交易日大幅下跌后，周四出现波动，投资者在权衡热门套利交易的平仓并考虑日本央行可能采取的利率路径，导致市场情绪脆弱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-firms-after-sharp-drop-traders-assess-japans-rate-path-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着机器人出租车的步伐加快，中国的司机和乘客都感到焦虑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-drivers-fret-robotaxis-pick-up-pace-passengers-2024-08-08/</link><description>刘毅是中国700万网约车司机之一。一名 36 岁的武汉居民今年开始兼职开车，当时全国范围内未售出公寓供过于求，建筑工程放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 00:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-drivers-fret-robotaxis-pick-up-pace-passengers-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：国防部长称韩国核武器将破坏美国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korean-nuclear-weapons-would-fracture-us-ties-defence-chief-says-2024-08-07/</link><description>韩国国防部长申元植（Shin Won-sik）对路透社表示，如果韩国开始制造核武器，韩国可能会破坏与美国的联盟，并冲击金融市场，他驳回了国内再次呼吁韩国拥有自己的核武库来威慑朝鲜的呼声。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korean-nuclear-weapons-would-fracture-us-ties-defence-chief-says-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行的信心消退，防御仍坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 21:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>举重——中国选手侯勇蝉联女子49公斤级冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-hou-retains-womens-49kg-title-2024-08-07/</link><description>中国选手侯智慧在周三的巴黎奥运会举重比赛中以206公斤的总成绩卫冕49公斤级奥运会举重冠军，最终战胜罗马尼亚选手米哈埃拉·坎贝。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 20:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-chinas-hou-retains-womens-49kg-title-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>花样游泳——中国队大比分领先美国队夺得杂技团体赛首金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/artistic-swimming-china-win-gold-team-event-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三，中国队在巴黎奥运会花样游泳项目上凭借生动活泼的杂技表演赢得了评委们的赞叹，并以总成绩遥遥领先美国队夺得银牌，夺得了首枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/artistic-swimming-china-win-gold-team-event-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔兹与中国的悠久历史引来攻击和赞扬</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/walzs-long-history-with-china-draws-attacks-praise-2024-08-07/</link><description>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选搭档、明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹正在引起美国共和党人和中国内部人士的关注，因为他与一个被视为华盛顿最大的经济和军事竞争对手的国家有着悠久的历史。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:41:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/walzs-long-history-with-china-draws-attacks-praise-2024-08-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>